LQuoteElement\"><code>HTMLQuoteElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLScriptElement\"><code>HTMLScriptElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLSelectElement\"><code>HTMLSelectElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLShadowElement\"><code>HTMLShadowElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLSourceElement\"><code>HTMLSourceElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLSpanElement\"><code>HTMLSpanElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLStyleElement\"><code>HTMLStyleElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableCaptionElement\"><code>HTMLTableCaptionElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableCellElement\"><code>HTMLTableCellElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableColElement\"><code>HTMLTableColElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement\"><code>HTMLTableElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableRowElement\"><code>HTMLTableRowElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableSectionElement\"><code>HTMLTableSectionElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTemplateElement\"><code>HTMLTemplateElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTextAreaElement\"><code>HTMLTextAreaElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTimeElement\"><code>HTMLTimeElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTitleElement\"><code>HTMLTitleElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTrackElement\"><code>HTMLTrackElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLUListElement\"><code>HTMLUListElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLUnknownElement\"><code>HTMLUnknownElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLVideoElement\"><code>HTMLVideoElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HashChangeEvent\"><code>HashChangeEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/History\"><code>History</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Location\"><code>Location</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MessageChannel\"><code>MessageChannel</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PageTransitionEvent\"><code>PageTransitionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Plugin\"><code>Plugin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PluginArray\"><code>PluginArray</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PopStateEvent\"><code>PopStateEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PromiseRejectionEvent\"><code>PromiseRejectionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RadioNodeList\"><code>RadioNodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ValidityState\"><code>ValidityState</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Erzeugt eine Base-64-kodierten ASCII-Zeichenkette aus einer \"Zeichenkette\" von Binärdaten.</p>\n\n<p>Hinweis: diese Funktion ist nicht für Raw-<a href=\"https://www.unicode.org/standard/WhatIsUnicode.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Unicode</a>-Zeichenketten geeignet (siehe Abschnitt \"Unicode-Zeichenketten\" unten).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var encodedData = window.btoa(<em>stringToEncode</em>);</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Example","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> encodedData <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">btoa</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Hello, world\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Zeichenkette kodieren</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> decodedData <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">atob</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>encodedData<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Zeichenkette dekodieren</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"hinweise","title":"Hinweise","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Diese Methode kann verwendet werden, um Daten zu kodieren, übertragen, und mittels<code> <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/atob\"><code>window.atob()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></code> wieder zu dekodieren, welche andernfalls Übertragungsprobleme bereiten würden. Beispielsweise ist es möglich, die Steuerzeichen mit den ASCII-Werten 0 bis 31 zu kodieren.</p>\n\n<p><code>btoa()</code> steht auch in JavaScript implementierten XPCOM-Komponenten zur Verfügung, auch wenn <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window\" title=\"DOM/window\"><code>window</code></a> in solchen Komponenten nicht das globale Objekt ist.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"unicode-zeichenketten","title":"Unicode-Zeichenketten","isH3":false,"content":"<p>In den meisten Browsern verursacht ein Aufruf von <code>window.btoa()</code> mit einer Unicode-Zeichenkette eine \"Character Out Of Range\"-Exception (\"Zeichen außerhalb des zulässigen Wertebereichs\").</p>\n\n<p>Das kann mithilfe eines solchen Code-Schemas vermieden werden (beigesteuert von <a class=\"external\" href=\"http://ecmanaut.blogspot.com/2006/07/encoding-decoding-utf8-in-javascript.html\" rel=\" noopener\">Johan Sundström</a>):</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">utf8_to_b64</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">str</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">btoa</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">unescape</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">encodeURIComponent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">b64_to_utf8</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">str</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">decodeURIComponent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">escape</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">atob</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Usage:</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">utf8_to_b64</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'✓ à la mode'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// JTI1dTI3MTMlMjUyMCUyNUUwJTI1MjBsYSUyNTIwbW9kZQ==</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">b64_to_utf8</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'JTI1dTI3MTMlMjUyMCUyNUUwJTI1MjBsYSUyNTIwbW9kZQ=='</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// \"✓ à la mode\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">utf8_to_b64</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'I \\u2661 Unicode!'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// SSUyNTIwJTI1dTI2NjElMjUyMFVuaWNvZGUlMjUyMQ==</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">b64_to_utf8</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'SSUyNTIwJTI1dTI2NjElMjUyMFVuaWNvZGUlMjUyMQ=='</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// \"I ♡ Unicode!\"</span>\n\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Eine günstigere, zuverlässigere und effizientere Lösung ist, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\" title=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMString\"><code>DOMString</code></a> zunächst in eine UTF-8-kodierte Zeichenkette zu konvertieren, die sich für <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Typed_arrays\" title=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Typed_arrays\">typed arrays</a> eignet. Eine Anleitung bietet <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Base64#solution_.232_.e2.80.93_rewriting_atob()_and_btoa()_using_typedarrays_and_utf-8\" title=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Base64_encoding_and_decoding#Solution_.232_.E2.80.93_rewriting_atob()_and_btoa()_using_TypedArrays_and_UTF-8\">dieser Abschnitt</a></strong>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/#dom-windowbase64-btoa\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'WindowBase64.btoa()' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>No change since the latest snapshot, <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html51/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"Die 'HTML 5.1' Spezifikation\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 5.1</a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html51/#dom-windowbase64-btoa\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 5.1<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'WindowBase64.btoa()' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>Snapshot of <a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"Die 'HTML Living Standard' Spezifikation\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard</a>. No change.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/#dom-windowbase64-btoa\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'WindowBase64.btoa()' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>Snapshot of <a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"Die 'HTML Living Standard' Spezifikation\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard</a>. Creation of <code>WindowBase64</code> (properties where on the target before it).</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Browser compatibility","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\"><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect3\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Wir konvertieren die Kompatibilitätsdaten in ein maschinenlesbares JSON Format</a></strong>.\n            Diese Kompatibilitätstabelle liegt noch im alten Format vor,\n            denn die darin enthaltenen Daten wurden noch nicht konvertiert.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Finde heraus wie du helfen kannst! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect4\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari (WebKit)</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td>1.0 (1.7 oder früher)[1]</td>\n   <td>10</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td>1.0 (1)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>[1] <code>btoa()</code> is also available to XPCOM components implemented in JavaScript, even though <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window\">window</a></code> is not the global object in components.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/docs/Web/API/WindowBase64/Base64_encoding_and_decoding\">Base64 encoding and decoding</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Basics_of_HTTP/Data_URLs\"><code>data</code> URIs</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/atob\"><code>window.atob()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Components.utils.importGlobalProperties\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">Components.utils.importGlobalProperties</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Example","id":"example"},{"text":"Hinweise","id":"hinweise"},{"text":"Unicode-Zeichenketten","id":"unicode-zeichenketten"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Erzeugt eine Base-64-kodierten ASCII-Zeichenkette aus einer \"Zeichenkette\" von Binärdaten.","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"btoa()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Cadenas binarias","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"WindowBase64.btoa()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope.btoa()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"btoa()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"WindowBase64.btoa()","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"WindowBase64.btoa()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"btoa()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"btoa()","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/btoa","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/btoa/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","tit